question_id: Tampilkan film yang belum pernah disewa oleh pelanggan mana pun.
sql_query:
SELECT
  f.title AS judul_film
FROM film AS f
WHERE
  NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT
      1
    FROM rental AS r
    WHERE
      r.film_id = f.film_id
  )
raw_response:
